        <text x="360" y="248" font-size="11" fill="#8a97ad" text-anchor="middle">— ทำงานแยกกันเงียบ ๆ หลังเวที "ไม่รู้ตัว" —</text>
        <path d="M90 176 Q120 120 280 104" fill="none" stroke="#9aa7bd" stroke-width="1.6" marker-end="url(#gw-up)"/>
        <path d="M230 176 Q250 130 300 108" fill="none" stroke="#9aa7bd" stroke-width="1.6" marker-end="url(#gw-up)"/>
        <path d="M510 176 Q490 130 440 108" fill="none" stroke="#9aa7bd" stroke-width="1.6" marker-end="url(#gw-up)"/>
